<plot>Short-lived show about Matt Burgess and his father Dick. Dick Burgess is a Broadway star who retires and goes to live with his son Matt who is running a small playhouse in rural Pennsylvania. Both men are stubborn which makes Matt's wife Chris the arbitrator. Other characters were Doc Sterling, the stage manager; Jillian, Matt's secretary; and Eric, Matt's helper.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?598663</url></doc>
